# NOTE: data/ski.db is deliberately NOT ignored. It is gitignored, but the image
# needs it as the seed snapshot that docker-entrypoint.sh copies onto an empty
# volume on first boot. Excluding it here would deploy an app with no history to
# grade against, and every mountain would score N/A until a full re-ingest.
